name: Tiny Elementals a unique multiplayer race game
blurb: Tiny Elementals - online multiplayer running game with unique graphics and amazing soundtrack for iOS and Android.

rewards.reward: Thank you very much for supporting our project.

As soon as our work sees the light of day you'll receive free digital copy of the game. We'll be also very honoured that you chose to support our project so we'll know that we are doing something that you like. Thank you.Thank you.

Our scribe will mark your name, using his magic fountain pen, on our wisdom center, called by the ancients: \u201eWebsite\u201d and the wind demon will announce your name to four corners of the world on \u201eFacebook\u201d.
Your head will sink in clouds of sounds sung by mermaids, acompanied by golem drums - you will receive digital copy of a soundtrack. You will also receive all rewards of the above.

Your name will be forged, with honour and glory, by fire and ice demons, in the hall of fame. Your name will be listed in the credits with special thanks. You'll be able to show it to your friends and say 'Look! Without me this game couldn't be done!' You will also receive all rewards of the above.
Our wizard will create a special image wich will be signed with your name. You will receive unique wallpaper with your name signed by our team. You will also receive all rewards of the above.

You'll gain acces to our secret room where magic is composed with technology. You will get a special ability to affect our developement machine. In other words, your vote and opinion will have the influence over how will the final game look like. Maybe you have new ideas which we could use? You will also receive all rewards of the above.
Your hands will get dirty - as the first ones you will get a playable version of the game. You'll enjoy privilige of being a beta tester. You will also receive all rewards of the above.

What is the best reward for playing an awesome game ? Enterteinment ? Fun ? Satisfaction ? Nothing to sneeze at - these are very important rewards. For your support you will get an opportunity to create you own in-game reward \u2013 an achivement. You will need to kickstart your creativity and design an achievment. You will also receive all above rewards.
You will create an object which will be placed in the game. Maybe you'll want to thank someone or make something funny? You will also receive every reward from beginning up to Beta Tester included.

Didn't you know that these monsters don't have names yet? They come to us every night and complain about names missing. Please save us from them (they can be really annoying) and think about how you could call them. You will also receive every reward up to Beta Tester (included).

The most powerful reward of all of them - you'll become a creator, designer and life giver. Maybe you have your favourite monster which should be here ? Or maybe you have a vivid imagination and have great ideas ? Or your child want his/her own monster ? Or you want to pride oneself in front of your friends ? Don't be shy - we will create a monster for you, all we need is an idea. You will also receive every reward from begining up to Beta Tester (included).
